\f3\b0\fs30 \cf20 With all that theory under our belts, let\'92s cement our understanding by actually creating a new namespace. The Linux\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://man7.org/linux/man-pages/man1/unshare.1.html"}}{\fldrslt 
