\pard\pardeftab720\sl540\sa450\partightenfactor0

\f3 \cf20 \cb3 \shad0 Now I run the following\'a0
\f14 \cf21 unshare
\f3 \cf20 \'a0command to create a new namespace with its own user and PID namespaces. I map the\'a0
\f14 \cf21 root
\f3 \cf20 \'a0user to the new namespace (in other words, I have\'a0
\f14 \cf21 root
\f3 \cf20 \'a0privilege within the new namespace), mount a new proc filesystem, and fork my process (in this case,\'a0
