\f11\b\fs44 \cf30 What Is NGINX?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa400\partightenfactor0

\f8\b0\fs32 \cf29 NGINX is open-source web server software used for reverse proxy, load balancing, and caching. It provides HTTPS server capabilities and is mainly designed for maximum performance and stability. It also functions as a proxy server for email communications protocols, such as IMAP, POP3, and SMTP.\'a0\
